description: Public key used to verify JSON Web Token signatures

kid.description: The unique identifier for the JSON Web Token, described in RFC 7517 Section 4.5

kty.description: The key type, described in RFC 7517 Section 4.1

use.description: The public key use, described in RFC 7517 Section 4.2

concreteType.description: Indicates which kind of JSON Web Key the object is, following the Synapse standard.
